> They're also guaranteed to be rewarded with a delicious, steakhouse-quality meal without leaving the comforts of their own kitchen. Case in point: this seared sirloin drizzled in a deluxe, sherry vinegar-spiked pan sauce with crispy, cheesy potato rounds, and a heap of roasted green beans.